word_group.brief_definition: 敏感性问题；涉及敏感问题

bilingual.source: The dog has a very sensitive nose.
bilingual.target: 这只狗有一个非常敏感的鼻子。

bilingual.source: The new smartphone has a touch-sensitive screen.
bilingual.target: 新款智能手机有一个触摸敏感的屏幕。

bilingual.source: Some people unfairly label sensitive men as nancy.
bilingual.target: 有些人不公平地把敏感的男人贴上娘娘腔的标签。

bilingual.source: Always store esd sensitive items in anti-static bags.
bilingual.target: 始终将对静电放电敏感的物品存放在防静电袋中。

bilingual.source: She bought unflavored toothpaste for her sensitive teeth.
bilingual.target: 她为她敏感的牙齿买了无味的牙膏。

bilingual.source: Store the temperature-sensitive medication in a cool place.
bilingual.target: 将这种对温度敏感的药物存放在阴凉处。

bilingual.source: The temperature-sensitive material changes color when heated.
bilingual.target: 这种对温度敏感的材料在加热时会变色。

bilingual.source: The artist uses a touch-sensitive tablet for digital drawing.
bilingual.target: 这位艺术家使用触摸敏感的平板进行数字绘画。

bilingual.source: The touch-sensitive pad on the laptop makes navigation simple.
bilingual.target: 笔记本电脑上的触摸敏感的板使导航变得简单。

bilingual.source: The temperature-sensitive equipment must be handled with care.
bilingual.target: 这种对温度敏感的设备必须小心处理。

list.abstract: Sensitive（英 [ˈsensətɪv]，美 [ˈsensətɪv]），英语单词，作形容词为敏感的；灵敏的；敏锐的。作名词为具有超自然通灵能力的人。短语搭配有be sensitive to（对…敏感）。例句为“They are sensitive to certain minerals.（它们对某些矿物质很敏感。）” Sensitive相关近义词有vulnerable、subtle等，相关反义词有insensitive、insensible。

yingyinNormal.en: My nipples are sensitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的乳头很敏感的。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, there's sensitive and there's too sensitive. Okay, what is too sensitive?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，敏感跟太敏感是有区别的。好吧，那什么是叫做太敏感呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, okay. See, that is the problem. He is too sensitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，看吧，那就是个问题 他太敏感了

yingyinNormal.en: Women love guys who love babies. It's that whole sensitive thing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女人爱喜欢宝宝的男人，这是感性的问题，懂了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Papa, please. Don't start. It was just a question. He's so sensitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 爸爸，拜托，不要再提这些了。只是随便问问，他太敏感了。

yingyinNormal.en: I do hope you will be careful with Bernard. He has a sensitive disposition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我希望你小心伯纳德，他的性情很敏感。

yingyinNormal.en: Money's a sensitive subject for Howie, because of the difference in our income.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我们收入有差距，所以华仔对钱这个话题很敏感。

yingyinNormal.en: In examining this new pressure-sensitive adhesive, I found more Dutch Gold Leaf.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对这个新的压敏胶黏剂进行试验之后，我发现了更多的荷兰金箔。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I like Vince a lot, you know? But, it's just Jason's so sensitive, you know?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很喜欢文斯，但杰森好感性。

yingyinNormal.en: I'll be in the car. You might want to change your shirt. They're very sensitive to smell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在车里等你，你得换件衣服了，她们对气味非常敏感。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, they must have all loved you very much. Look, Ross, he's just, Sandy's just sensitive. That's all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们一定都很喜欢你。听着，罗斯，珊帝只不过是很敏感，不过是如此。

yingyinNormal.en: What? Too sensitive to take care of our baby? No, I mean, that guy… These are amazing! Sandy made madeleines.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太敏感就不能照顾我们的小孩吗？不，我是说，那个男的… 这真是太好吃了！珊帝做的马德琳饼干。

yingyinNormal.en: Now that I've given you this incredibly sensitive and highly classified information, what do you think, Toretto?
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在我已经给你提供了如此有效且高度机密的信息，你有什么打算，多雷托？

yingyinNormal.en: And in the long run, I think sensitive it's just better than having just like a really, really, really nice butt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 长期来说，感性应该比身材很猛来得好。

yingyinNormal.en: And he's being Mr. Joe Sensitive, and she starts thinking: Maybe this is the guy for me, because he understands me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是体帖入微先生，她在想“也许他就是我的伴侣，他这么了解我”。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, I haven't told him about it. We've been getting so much more funding than physics, he's been a little sensitive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实我还没告诉他呢。我们这边获得的经费比物理那边多太多了，他对此略为敏感。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't need a destination when you're running on an omnidirectional treadmill with quadraphonic, pressure-sensitive underlay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只要你脚下有一台四声道压敏底垫全方位跑步机你就可以随时出发。

yingyinNormal.en: So, how you doing? A little sensitive, but not bad. Does it always take that long? No, they usually don't have to go out and get more wax.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感觉如何？有点小敏感，但还好，一般都需要这么长时间的吗？不，他们一般不需要跑去多拿点蜜蜡。

yingyinNormal.en: It's about this sensitive girl who comes to L.A. from Lincoln, Nebraska, to be an actress and winds up a waitress at the cheesecake factory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 讲一个多愁善感的女生从内布拉斯加州的林肯来到了洛杉矶，她本想当名演员，最终却在乳酪蛋糕店当了服务生。

yingyinNormal.en: So much so, that people who are more anxious or socially conservative are often more sensitive to stink than their adventure seeking friends.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以那些容易紧张或是不善交际的人，会很在意自己的味道，而不敢冒险交朋友。

examination_example.sentence: The sensors (传感器) in the electrodes are very <highlight>sensitive</highlight> and catch the electrical activity that takes place in the brain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电极上的传感器非常灵敏，可以捕捉大脑中发生的电活动。

examination_example.sentence: To avoid interferences, and keep the telescopes <highlight>sensitive</highlight>, radio telescopes are built in places where there are no human radio waves or electronic signals.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了避免干扰，并保持望远镜的灵敏度，射电望远镜建在没有人类无线电波或电子信号的地方。

examination_example.sentence: To make an amplifier <highlight>sensitive</highlight> enough, it is usually cooled to, very low temperatures.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为了使放大器足够灵敏，通常要将其冷却到非常低的温度。

examination_example.sentence: Being culturally <highlight>sensitive</highlight> is important.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对文化敏感是很重要的。

examination_example.sentence: I'm also not as <highlight>sensitive</highlight> as I used to be-getting an impolite customer might make me feel bad, but very soon I can laugh it off with my co-workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我也不再像以前那样敏感了——遇到不礼貌的客户可能会让我感觉不好，但很快我就会和同事一笑置之。
